id: monica-output-escaping
title: Agent output escaping is incomplete
description: TOON quoted strings and Markdown table cells escape delimiters without first escaping existing backslashes.
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 1
tags[4]: agent-ux,codeql,correctness,formatters
created_at: "2026-07-16T16:59:36.808Z"
updated_at: "2026-07-16T17:19:31.615Z"
deadline: "2026-07-19T16:59:36.808Z"
closed_at: "2026-07-16T17:19:31.613Z"
author: codex-root
estimated_minutes: 90
acceptance_criteria: TOON escapes backslashes and quotes deterministically; Markdown escapes backslashes and pipes; existing formatter snapshots remain compatible
definition_of_ready: Dismissed CodeQL alerts #6 and #7 are reproduced at the formatter helper level.
parent: monica-security-modernization
reviewer: unbraind
risk: medium
confidence: 95
sprint: 2026-07-security-modernization
release: next
reporter: Source security audit
severity: medium
environment: all formatted CLI output
repro_steps: Format a value containing backslash followed by quote or pipe.
resolution: "Escape existing backslashes before TOON quotes and Markdown pipes, with focused regression tests."
expected_result: TOON and Markdown output deterministically preserve literal backslashes and delimiters.
actual_result: Formatter regression tests pass within the 542-test suite and the merged implementation handles backslash-plus-delimiter edge cases.
affected_version: 2026.3.6-2
component: formatters
regression: false
customer_impact: Machine consumers can misparse edge-case CRM text.
dependencies[1]{id,kind,created_at,author,source_kind}:
  monica-security-modernization,related,"2026-07-16T16:59:36.808Z",null,null
comments[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T16:59:36.808Z",codex-root,This is correctness hardening; the dismissed security classification does not remove the malformed-output risk.
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T16:59:36.808Z",codex-root,Escape backslash first to avoid escaping the escape inserted for the delimiter.
learnings[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T16:59:36.808Z",codex-root,Output formats consumed by agents need deterministic escaping even when the content is not rendered as executable code.
files[2]{path,scope,note}:
  src/formatters/toon.ts,project,TOON escaping
  src/formatters/markdown.ts,project,Markdown escaping
tests[1]{command,scope,note}:
  bun test tests/formatters.test.ts,project,formatter regression suite
docs[1]{path,scope,note}:
  docs/OUTPUT-SCHEMAS.md,project,machine output contract
close_reason: Formatter hardening merged in PR #45
body: Values such as backslash-quote in TOON or backslash-pipe in Markdown can remain ambiguous or malformed. Escape backslashes before quotes or pipes and add exact regression tests.
